@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

[*] --> AccountCreated

state AccountCreated
state WatchingVideos
state UploadingVideo
state SavingVideo
state ViewingSavedVideos
state InDiscussion

AccountCreated --> WatchingVideos : [account created]
WatchingVideos --> SavingVideo : [save video to likes list]
SavingVideo --> WatchingVideos

WatchingVideos --> ViewingSavedVideos : [view saved videos]
ViewingSavedVideos --> WatchingVideos

WatchingVideos --> UploadingVideo : [upload video]
UploadingVideo --> WatchingVideos : [video uploaded]

WatchingVideos --> InDiscussion : [enter discussion option]
InDiscussion --> WatchingVideos : [exit discussion]

@enduml
